cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a new method for pose estimation based on visual data.
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the method can be applied to robotic systems for pose estimation.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the method involves optimization and least squares problems.
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the method involves linear matrix inequalities and constraints.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the method can use visual appearance data in addition to point cloud data.
